column2: Tu Roop Ki Rani Tu Choron Ka Raja
Mere Dil Mein Tu Hi Tu Hai
Tum Itna Jo Muskura Rahe Ho
Tum Ko Dekha To Yeh Khayal Aaya
Yeh Tera Ghar Yeh Mera Ghar
Apne Liye Jiye To Kya Jiye
Har Taraf Ab Yehi Afsane Hain
Ek Do Teen Char Aur Panch
Waqt Ne Kiya Kya Haseen Sitam
Teri Nigahon Pe Mar Mar Gaye Ham
Tera Husn Rahe Mera Ishq Rahe
Mile Na Phool To Kanton Se Dosti
Hai Kali Kali Ke Lab Par
Yeh Teri Saadgi Yeh Tera Bankpan
Main Yeh Sochkar Uske Dar Se Utha
Ja Ri Pawaniya Piya Ke Des Ja
Kyun Mujhe Itni Khushi De Di
Tere Jhoote Vade Ka Aitbar Kiya
Pyas Kuchh Aur Bhi Bhadka Di
Jis Din Se Maine Tumko Dekha
San San San Woh Chali Hawa
Bol Baby Bol Rock N Roll
Kuchh Dil Ne Kaha Kuchh Bhi Nahin
Betaab Dil Ki Tamanna Yehi Hai
Milo Na Tum To Hum Ghabraye
Aaj Socha To Ansoo Bahr Aaye
Do Dil Toote Do Dil Haare
Do Din Ki Zindagi Kaisi Yeh Zindagi
Jeet Hi Lenge Baazi Hum Tum
